The sled.

236
00:19:50,175 --> 00:19:54,552
Look, John Hancock's
writing his name in the snow!

237
00:19:58,934 --> 00:20:03,347
Do you want to be held back a grade?
Concentrate, man!

238
00:20:11,697 --> 00:20:14,188
Later, Mrs. K.

239
00:20:16,994 --> 00:20:21,406
Please turn in your exam, Bart.
Class is over.

240
00:20:21,624 --> 00:20:25,039
-Could you grade it now?
-Well, all right.

241
00:20:25,294 --> 00:20:27,963
Let me get Old Red.

242
00:20:32,968 --> 00:20:35,720
